column1: Last name Field is accepting numbers as Input under add new feature of Customers Module.
column27:
Last name Field is accepting numbers as Input under add new feature of Customers Module.

Steps to Reproduce -
1. Login to Uniform Website.
2. Go to the Customers Module.
3. Click on the Add new Button.
4. Input Alphanumeric Characters in Last name field.
5. Click on save button.

Input test Data -
asd123

Expected Result - 
Validation message "Last name should only consist Alphabets" should appear

Actual output - 
Input is accepted.
